# Build context is the repo root. Keep the image lean & reproducible — never copy host-built
# artifacts, secrets, or forensic evidence into the build. npm ci runs INSIDE the image and
# fetches the correct linux-native binaries (e.g. sharp), so host node_modules must be excluded.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.env
cases/
addon/
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github
.planning
.gstack
docs
*.md
companion/prompts
# Atomic-write temp files (see .gitignore).
*.tmp
*.tmp.*
